Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:20.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}さぁ選べ  舞い降りた天使達
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}感じる予感に Shoot the arrow of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:27.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}翼に意志を 身を委ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}倦まず弛まず
